Anki
-------------------------------------

Prerequisites for Linux/FreeBSD/etc:

- Python 2.5+
- Python-Qt/PyQt 4.6+
- SimpleJSON 1.7.3+
- Beautiful Soup

For audio playing support:

- mplayer

For audio recording support:

- pyaudio
- lame

